HEADWORD: Unconsidered
<hw>Un`con*sid"ered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not considered
or attended to; not regarded; inconsiderable; trifling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A snapper-up of <qex>unconsidered</qex> trifles.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unconsonant</ent>⟦br⟧
